\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 ME\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 How many people have been in a situation like that?\
In most relationships you are either one or the other!  \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Relationships are tough and we\'92re starting a new series as we launch this new church on relationships.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 WE
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We are in relationship with everything around us\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our family and friends\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The people we love and hate\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But also other things too\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our cars\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our jobs\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some are healthy and some are unhealthy relationships\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We say things like \'91I love my car\'92 and \'91I love Chick-fil-e\'92!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b\fs28 \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is how we are wired!  It\'92s a good things\'85we were made for that.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 Transition:  While we are in relationship with everything\'85ONE RELATIONSHIP AFFECTS EVERY OTHER RELATIONSHIP\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 BT \'96 One relationship affects every other relationship\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 And we know this inherently!\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It can be both good and bad:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I met a girl\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We had a boy\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I got a new job!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is why we lie to ourselves and say things like:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If I could just get some more money then I would be ok\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If I could just find a spouse who loves me\'85I don\'92t care about anything else.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If I could just get a better job\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If I could lose weight or get in shape\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We say to ourselves that if this one area is ok then everything else will be great.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We have a relationship with everything in our lives\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This one area affects everything else\'85the problem is for many of us we\'92re looking in the wrong area\'85and it always leaves us short.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf4 Transition:  The problem is it always comes up short!\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You know that because you\'92ve gotten all those things you\'92ve said that about.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You finally got a job\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You finally found a spouse\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You finally had a kid\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You finally got more money\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Etc\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf4 Transition:  The reason it continually fail us is we only dealing with symptoms not causes\'85and if we never start to deal with root causes\'85we\'92ll end up like the woman on the video.  Always wondering and never knowing.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 We live in a broken world:\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is death everywhere \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We instinctively understand there is something fundamentally wrong with how life works on this planet\'85this we feel it.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Yet because of the nail\'85we live in this broken world.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf5 For the wages of sin is death\'85  Romans 6:23\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf3 (Sit here for a  second Nic)\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf4 Trasnsition:  He goes onto say the world is even more messed up than this\'85\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs18 \cf5 \super 15\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub I do not understand what I do. For what I want to do I do not do, but what I hate I do.\'a0
\f3\b\fs18 \super 16\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub And if I do what I do not want to do, I agree that the law is good.  Romans 7:15-16\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Essentially he is saying every time you do something you don\'92t want to do you are agreeing there is something more to this world.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You were made for something more!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some people here today you have a secret\'85you are so torn on the inside it is killing you.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1
\f0\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If anyone knew what I really thought about, looked at, drank, took, went to, spent my time\'85\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Paul says your torments agrees with God that there is something more here.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf4 Transition:  As broken as the world is there is a solution and it is not to medicate you through it and hope it all gets better.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs27 \cf5 Christ Jesus came into the world\'a0to save sinners. 1 Tim 1:15\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The key word there is WORLD!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}One relationship changed every other relationship!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s what we have been talking about it today\'85the world!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It was broken and Jesus came to reconcile it to Him\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 19\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For God was pleased\'a0to have all his fullness\'a0dwell in him,\'a0
\f3\b\fs18 \super 20\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and through him to reconcile\'a0to himself all things, whether things on earth or things in heaven,\'a0by making peace through his blood,\'a0shed on the cross.  Colossians 1\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf4 Transition:  To put it a different way\'85\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs18 \cf5 \super 5\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But he was pierced\'a0for our transgressions,\uc0\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 he was crushed\'a0for our iniquities;\uc0\u8232 the punishment\'a0that brought us peace\'a0was on him,\u8232 
\fs10 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\fs24 and by his wounds\'a0we are healed.\uc0\u8232 Isaiah 53:5\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b\fs28 \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can be healed today and not just helped\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t need HELP \'96 you need to be HEALED\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And when it says \'91pierced\'92 it means there was a nail!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}IT\'92S ALL ABOUT THE NAIL!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0  \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f5\b\fs28 \cf4 Transition:  I want ask our host team to hand out something to everyone\'85\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you are here today and you don\'92t have a personal relationship with Jesus I want to let you in on a little secret\'85we are here for you!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Because every one of us at one point in time has live life on the surface only dealing with the symptoms of life and never dealing with the deeper issue.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And we all came to the conclusion that one relationship, a relationship with Jesus Christ as your Lord and Savior changes every relationship you have with everything!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What you\'92re getting is a representation of the nail that is inside every person at some point in time.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I want you to feel the weight of it in your hand.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you\'92re here today and you\'92ve never put your faith in Jesus as your savior then you are carrying this around with you wherever you go.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 Definition of Insanity is doing the same thing over and over again and expecting different results\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have a decision to make today that each of us have to make at some point in life.  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Where do I want the nail!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f0\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s about the nail whether we want to acknowledge it or not\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Whether we want to keep it surfacey or not\'85it\'92s about the nail!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There\'92s a nail\'85where do you want it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}As you walk out of here today I want you to know you can be free from sin and the nail.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can leave it here.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can be FREE!\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
